Class ReifyStrategy

java.lang.Object
  awesome.platform.ReifyStrategy

public class ReifyStrategy
extends java.lang.Object

Holds various reify strategies. Use one of the constants here as the value for the AwReify annotation.

Constant Field Values

SUPPRESS_ALL

public static final java.lang.String SUPPRESS_ALL
Applicable for all types (classes, methods, constructors and fields). Suppresses reify of all shadows: those in the type's level and below (if exists).

See Also:
Constant Field Values

SUPPRESS_WITHIN

public static final java.lang.String SUPPRESS_WITHIN
Applicable for methods and constructors. Suppresses reify of shadow within the body only.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

SUPPRESS_EXECUTION_SHADOW

public static final java.lang.String SUPPRESS_EXECUTION_SHADOW
Applicable for methods and constructors (TODO also classes). Suppresses reify of the outer shadow, whether it is a method-execution shadow or a constructor-execution shadows. Shadows within the body are exposed.

Constant Field Values

SUPPRESS_STATICINITIALIZATION

public static final java.lang.String SUPPRESS_STATICINITIALIZATION
Applicable for classes. Suppresses reify of the staticinitialization shadow (the shadow and within).
